If 10+2/graduate/post-graduate qualified Saksham Yuva who fails to attend to/report to any honorary assignment he/she is nominated for within 3 days then:-
a)	In the first instance, if he/she fails to report within 7 days, then the unemployment allowance shall be discontinued and his/her name shall be kept in abeyance/debar from the list of beneficiaries for one month;
b)	In the second instance, if he/she fails to report within 7 days, then the unemployment allowance shall be discontinued and his/her name shall be kept in abeyance/debar from the list of beneficiaries for one year;
c)	In the third instance, if he/she fails to report within 7 days, then he/she will be rejected permanently from the scheme.
